Also, I get to look forward to my high level gear sucking since it has like +40 spirit, as they never changed the gear after nerfing spirit. I rarely have the luxury of using the 5 second rule, even when grouped, as I'm either healing or nuking or dropping totems. Maybe it will be useful on raids, but I doubt it.<br />
<br />
It is absolutely useless for PVP also.</div>
